dc_description_s: This data layer represents addresses for Clark County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Clark_Addresses_2014.gdb'. [The rural address system runs on a N and W grid from the south east corner of the county. All unincorporated municipalties use the county rural address grid. The address number for a location represents the intersection of entrance from the public road. No address numbers are given from a private road.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
